Paladins are long accustomed to fighting with the aid of a mount.  After<br>
years of buying and training these special companions, a very skilled<br>
paladin is able to use their bond with their god to summon just the right<br>
mount.  Although a number of different reagents can be used to summon<br>
their ideal mount, a wise paladin selects the correct one without error. <br>
